<h2>I found a Bug!</h2>

<p>Nice one! Contentify is still in an early stage of development. A beta software is the most natural habitation of bugs. So, if you find a bug, please let us know! Knowing where they life is the first step to hunt them down. If you want to help us, then please send us a mail. The more information describing the bug you provide, the faster we will find it. Screeenshots are very welcome.</p>